Total Petroleum Ghana to Pay 0.48 Cedis a Share Interim Dividend

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-10-11T11:29:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/total-petroleum-ghana-to-pay-0-48-cedis-a-share-interim-dividend.html
Total Petroleum Ghana Ltd. (TOTAL)  said it
plans to pay an interim dividend of 0.48 cedis per share.  The company, a unit of  Total SA (FP) , commented in a statment
published on the website of the Ghana Stock Exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Moses Mozart Dzawu in Accra at 
